lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth withstood heavy winds and even stiffer challenges to remain atop the Masters leaderboard, and will take a one-shot lead into Sunday's final round as he bids to complete a successful defence of his Green Jacket.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Stays Top at Masters Despite Late Stumble
